Monitor Your Pricing Data From the Operations Console
Get a complete overview of the pricing data from the Operations Console. At a glance, you see the data consumed when pricing operations are performed and the event log files generated during the execution of pricing processes.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.
How: To generate event log files, from Setup, under Event Monitoring Settings, turn on Generate event log files.
title: Monitor Pricing Data from the Operations Console
